def matrix_multiply(a, b): result = []; for i in range(len(a)): row = []; for j in range(len(b[0])): sum_val = sum(a[i][k] * b[k][j] for k in range(len(b))); row.append(sum_val); result.append(row); return result

class PerformanceOptimizer: def __init__(self): self.cache = {}; def memoize(self, func): def wrapper(n): if n in self.cache: return self.cache[n]; result = func(n); self.cache[n] = result; return result; return wrapper
async def parallel_process(tasks): import asyncio; results = await asyncio.gather(*[process(task) for task in tasks]); return results

def trie_implementation(): class TrieNode: def __init__(self): self.children = {}; self.is_end = False; def insert(self, word): node = self; for char in word: if char not in node.children: node.children[char] = TrieNode(); node = node.children[char]; node.is_end = True; return TrieNode()
